{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require clubs only sell drinks in cups with one-way flow",
        "additional_details": "There is an alarming number of incidences where people have been spiked whilst out clubbing/in a club and therefore being put into dangerous situations. Having one-way flowing cups should help to decrease the number of people consuming drinks that have been spiked or tampered with.\r\n \r\nMany of these individuals who suffer from being spiked do not receive the required help from club staff.",
        "background": "Make it a legal requirement for clubs to only sell drinks with one-way flow in order to make spiking drinks much harder. There are a range of cups that enable people to drink from them, without the risk of their drink being tampered with.",
